dct_title_s: De heylige wytvermaerde stadt Ierusalem eerst genaemt Salem
dct_alternative_sm: De heylige wytvermaerde stadt Jerusalem eerst genaemt Salem Genesis 14. ver 18
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Features illustrations of structures, people, and crucifixions.
Shows topography, vegetation, drainage, places of historical interest.
Includes index: Verklaringe der cyfer getale.
Descriptive text, e.g.: Dese kaerte wert gestelt voor het 3 cap. Nehemiae.
